# PassGo - Multipass VM Manager

- Go TUI using Bubble Tea (Elm architecture)
- Single package `main`
- Root model in main.go routes to child models by viewState
- Async work via tea.Cmd returning typed Msg in messages.go
- Styling via lipgloss in styles.go; themes in themes.go
- See ARCHITECTURE.md for data flow, file map, message flow, and view state machine
